Package: date.reader
Title: This packages extends type.convert and read.table to automatically detect
    and coerce date fields to POSIX.
Version: 0.2
Author: "DecisionPatterns [aut, cre]"
Maintainer: Daryl McCullough <dmcullough@decisionpatterns.com>
Description: date.reader provides replacement type.convert and read.table
    methods that will automatically recognize and parse dates as POSIXct dates
    using the lubridate package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    lubridate (>= 1.3.3)
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: true
